comments: Poole (WAS) brushes Durant's (PHX) arm and marginal contact occurs at the start of his drive.
While defending the shot attempt. Avdija (WAS) makes contact with Durant's (PHX) lower body, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Booker (PHX) fumbles ball after he momentarily bring both hands to it while dribbling.

Replay review of the foul called on Booker (PHX) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful, as replay confirmed Booker makes clean contact with the ball. However his teammate Allen (PHX) reaches in and initiates contact to Avdija's (WAS) arm during the play near the basket.
Gafford (WAS) establishes himself in Gordon's (PHX) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Nurkic (PHX) does not establishes himself in Jones' (WAS) path and extends his lower body to deliver illegal contact.
Booker (PHX) contests the driving shot attempt and marginal body contact occurs with Jones (WAS) after the release.
Gafford (WAS) initiates contact to Durant's (PHX) head during his shot attempt at the rim.
Allen (PHX) legally contests Poole's (WAS) jump shot attempt.

Replay review of the foul called on Booker (PHX) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. The call on the floor was overturned as replay confirmed Booker (PHX) legally contests Kuzma's (WAS) jump shot attempt.
Kuzma (WAS) commits a take foul on Durant (PHX).
Kuzma (WAS) commits a take foul on Gordon (PHX).
Poole (WAS) releases and makes marginal contact with Allen (PHX) off ball.
